comment.content: T2 at Mumbai Chhatrapati Shivaji airport looks fancy from the inside out but lacks finesse. The security check is horrible because of the design and the CISF personnel who man the checkpoints. The views from the food court are lovely. The free WiFi is decently fast, though it works only for half an hour.
